query BetsPlaced($where: BetPlaced_filter) {
  betPlaceds(where: $where) {
    chainName
    gameId
    bettor
    number
    value
    timestamp
    betId
    blockNumber
    blockTimestamp
    transactionHash
  }
}
4ea33ed8ed756e9a58174f17f3d63f723f3fef04:
query PrizePayments($where: PrizePayment_filter) {
  prizePayments(where: $where) {
    chainName
    gameId
    betId
    bettor
    requestedBy
    drawnNumber
    prizeValue
    timestamp
    blockNumber
    blockTimestamp
    transactionHash
  }
}
